gt_text: 上午10:00 — 构建伦理大模型 — Mariah Singh博士 — 203室 上午11:15 — 量子芯片的未来 — Anton Yu教授 — 主会场 下午1:00 — 快闪演讲：人工智能与艺术 下午2:30 — 小组讨论：开源与专有模型 下午3:45 — C厅：初创展示（提供小吃！） 闭门会议：仅限受邀者 — 305室 导师咨询展台 — 开放时间：9:30–4:00 免费WiFi：请用胸牌编号登录 提醒：请于下午5点前通过App提交反馈 今晚派对：4层天台，晚上7点开始
juding_criteria:
Here is a list of every concrete visual element the final image must contain:

*   Technology conference venue hallway
*   Large printed schedule wall
*   Laminated A3 posters (covering the wall)
*   Columns of posters
*   Color-coded posters
*   Straight-pinned posters
*   Slightly skewed posters
*   Legible Chinese text: '上午10:00 — 构建伦理大模型 — Mariah Singh博士 — 203室' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '上午11:15 — 量子芯片的未来 — Anton Yu教授 — 主会场' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '下午1:00 — 快闪演讲：人工智能与艺术' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '下午2:30 — 小组讨论：开源与专有模型' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '下午3:45 — C厅：初创展示（提供小吃！）' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '闭门会议：仅限受邀者 — 305室' (on a poster)
*   Legible Chinese text: '导师咨询展台 — 开放时间：9:30–4:00' (on a poster or sign)
*   Legible Chinese text: '免费WiFi：请用胸牌编号登录' (on a poster or sign)
*   Legible Chinese text: '提醒：请于下午5点前通过App提交反馈' (on a poster or sign)
*   Legible Chinese text: '今晚派对：4层天台，晚上7点开始' (on a poster or sign)
*   Conference signage typography (for all listed text)
*   QR codes (on some posters/signage)
*   Sponsor logos (on some posters/signage)
*   Directional arrows (on some posters/signage)
*   Man (facing and reading the schedule wall)
*   Lanyard badge (held by or on the man)
*   Tote bag (held by the man)
*   Woman (beside man, facing wall, photographing a poster)
*   Phone (held by woman, aimed at a poster)
*   Open hallway (leading deeper into the venue, visible beyond characters)
